      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great overall, though it does show minor surface blemishes and small stone chips consistent with its age and regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only light wear on the driver's seat and touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is solid, having received regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance, ensuring a reliable driving experience for the next owner. It offers a great balance of value and performance for anyone looking for a dependable pre-owned vehicle.",
