    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, making it a suitable candidate for a dedicated project or as a parts donor. The engine currently runs roughly and will likely require a significant overhaul, and the transmission is showing signs of failure with noticeable slipping. Externally, the car has suffered from neglect, featuring widespread paint oxidation, several large dents, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the cabin requires a complete detailing and repair, as the upholstery is heavily torn and the electronics are largely unresponsive.",
