      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape. It drives like a dream and looks even better. I'm really looking for someone who will appreciate a ride this clean. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
