    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, this specimen represents the pinnacle of the S54-powered era. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six exhibits perfect compression and instantaneous throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The Double VANOS timing is precise, and the rod bearing service has been performed proactively. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with mechanical bolt-action precision, feeding a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec bushings that maintain original kinematic integrity. Finished in rare Laguna Seca Blue with flawless paint depth, this is a turn-key investment for the serious collector demanding mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
