    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks to be found. Every body panel aligns perfectly with factory-tight tolerances. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' fragrance; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear or creasing, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history fully documented from mile one. It has been strictly hand-washed and has never seen inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Sale includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover.",
      "price": 43500.0,
